Rattrap:





Rattrap looked back as the cat went straight past him. He picked his 
head up and watched as she ran for a clearing. "What is goin' on?" He 
thought of going after her and figuring this whole thing 
out. "Curiousity killed da cat." He blinked. "But I ain't a cat." He 
pinned his ears back and sighed. "Rattrap, Maxi--" He 
stopped. "Right." He remembered that he was a Predacon last he 
transformed. "Terrorize." He transformed to his robot mode. The 
activation code made him feel rusted. He turned and ran out to the 
edge of the clearing.
